        <briefdescription>
<para>Processes all shooting entities and spawns projectiles. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>For each entity with ShootComponent, Aim2DComponent, and TranslationStateComponent:</para>
<para>1. Skips if aim frequency or intensity are near zero 2. Accumulates `deltaTime * intensity` into the cooldown timer 3. If timer &lt; cooldownDelta, updates timer and continues 4. Calculates projectile count as `floor(timer / cooldownDelta)` 5. Reduces timer by `count * cooldownDelta` 6. Enqueues SpawnCommands with <ref refid="structhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1types_1_1EmitterContext" kindref="compound">EmitterContext</ref> for each projectile</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>updateContext</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The current frame&apos;s update context. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
